reut2-017.sgm, USSR ATTENDS ADB MEET, UNCERTAIN ON MEMBERSHIP, The Soviet Union is attending anAsian Development Bank (ADB) annual general meeting for thefirst time, but has not decided whether to apply formembership, a senior Soviet State Bank official said.    No specific plans exist for applying for membership

column8:
