reut2-017.sgm, U.S. CORPORATE FINANCE - FINANCING SURGE SEEN, U.S. corporate treasurers are expectedto race to market this week, propelled by hopes that the recentrecoveries of the Treasury market and the dollar will whetinvestors' appetities for new issues, underwriters said.    Underwriters expect to price about 2.3 billion dlrs of newdebt issues this week, including an asset-backed debt deal.    Treasurers have been sitting on the sidelines for weeks

column25:
