reut2-017.sgm, INVESTORS MAY TAKE COMPUTERLAND PUBLIC, The investor group that has agreed tobuy &lt;Computerland Corp> will likely take the leading personalcomputer retailer public or sell it to other investors,industry analysts said.    Now's a good time

